net::ip_addr::Ipv4Addr::octets.doc:
Returns the four eight-bit integers that make up this address.

# Examples

```
use std::net::Ipv4Addr;

let addr = Ipv4Addr::new(127, 0, 0, 1);
assert_eq!(addr.octets(), [127, 0, 0, 1]);
```

